{"tid":668688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約法院第三度拒絕何志平保釋申請","createTime":"2018-05-18T00:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T05:30:43.000Z","uid":22054,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e43ae97e2b80dfbebfbea6ee073dfbc17ccbcfd2","tid":668688,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:17:55.000Z","msg":"紐約法院第三度拒絕何志平保釋申請<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=306214&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D306214%26refer%3Dshare&d=sYyeQcIbHTNM7RPHhJDkp2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=a81037e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D306214%26refer%3Dshare&h=789d3bf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=306214&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在美國紐約被還柙的前民政事務局局長何志平，第三度申請保釋被拒。<br />\n<br />\n法官早前提出多個問題，包括要求控辯雙方釐清何志平能否以香港物業作為抵押，並就其刑期及潛逃風險再作詳細評估。<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約法院在當地時間周四再開庭處理，何志平一方日前向法院提交文件稱，願意將用作抵押的物業屋契帶到美國交予法庭，一旦何志平棄保潛逃，法庭便可把屋契交予美國政府充公及變賣，又將保釋金額提高至300萬美元，<span style=\"color: red;\">但法官指出，現時何志平的律師費是由涉案能源公司支付，認為他獲該公司財政上支持，難以評估其背後的財力，而充公境外物業耗時，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認為任何資產抵押皆無法確保何志平不會潛逃。</span></span>加上刑期方面，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">辯方最新估計何志平若被定罪將被判監12至15年</span></strong>，法官認為何志平潛逃風險較高，拒絕其保釋申請，案件將在11月開審。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7229c26b19df7f8a0a37bc3cff459aa5b0e31ba","tid":668688,"uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:18:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">国家英雄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93555eef9041b44530e1b8347a48bf715e03b9e6","tid":668688,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:19:09.000Z","msg":"押埋間能源公司先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61de744a45807a3ae7dfacbf479399e21baaa1cd","tid":668688,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:36:11.000Z","msg":"前民政事務局局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6665a954f76105d1e8ff77a3389aed57398cd85","tid":668688,"uid":70846,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:48:26.000Z","msg":"仲恰下恰下以為美國佬要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地係唔信你唔會棄保潛逃<br />\n一日泊著中共呢個碼頭，一日都坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5b59adc0801a6a51be0b81cd32d61629c363bd","tid":668688,"uid":65061,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"還有黨<br />\n侵我中華者，雖遠必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848dd2b0da28431f2699d29d136ef3a6a03999de","tid":668688,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecbbe262d8b9c64580cbb5ce92c4802b7825242","tid":668688,"uid":112232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"到底吳京幾時先肯出動"},{"pid":"d8ab3d7c454f22f4f290e674f6cad05a6e24af27","tid":668688,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:53:38.000Z","msg":"屎眼大開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17027f023f54e6d3c9d5fb614f46ee3de998c024","tid":668688,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05